\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 Outcome
\f0\b0  
\f1\b A smarter tool for a more human interaction
\f0\b0 \
The redesigned interface gave call center agents a clearer, faster, and more confident way to prepare for every call. By surfacing AI-assisted customer insights at the right moment, the tool reduced cognitive load and supported agents in delivering more personalized service \'97 turning a fragmented experience into a unified, intuitive workflow.\
