\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Fully editable Sketch file for future iterations\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 Outcome
\f0\b0  
\f1\b From workaround to workflow
\f0\b0 \
The new scrum board gave procurement managers a centralized, flexible space to run their calls without switching between tools. By bringing the information into the platform itself, the design reduced manual effort, improved visibility across the team, and made collaboration during scrum sessions faster and more structured.\
