\f0\b0  
\f1\b A hiring process that scales with the business
\f0\b0 \
The platform gave each stakeholder a clear, purpose-built experience \'97 reducing friction across the hiring pipeline and bringing structure to a process that had outgrown its previous tools. By designing for multiple roles within a single system, the tool supported faster, more coordinated hiring decisions.}